# Generated Windows resource files. The per-arch icon resources under
# cmd/morgue are committed so every `go build` (incl. GoReleaser, which never
# runs go-winres) embeds the app icon into the released exe. Ignore stray syso
# elsewhere, but keep the committed icon resources for the release arches.
*.syso
!cmd/morgue/rsrc_windows_amd64.syso
!cmd/morgue/rsrc_windows_arm64.syso

